table.name:
SELECT app_country_dependency_id
       , product_id
       , product_name
       , country_id
       , country_name
       , dependent_on_country_id
       , dependent_on_country
       , dependent_on_country_id_2
       , dependent_on_country_2
       , dependent_on_country_id_3
       , dependent_on_country_3
       , dependent_on_country_id_4
       , dependent_on_country_4
       , dependent_on_country_id_5
       , dependent_on_country_5
       , dependent_on_tracking_date_id
       , dependent_on_date
       , start_tracking_date_id
       , start_tracking_date
       , end_tracking_date_id
       , end_tracking_date
       , is_dependent_on_the_core
       , license_num
       , dependency_type
       , date_updated
       , date_created
       , is_active
       , extract_date
 FROM gpdip_prd.gpdip_uddl_regulatory.pfleet_country_dependency
where tracking_path = 'Label Text Driven' and country_name != 'ALL PRESENTATIONS' and is_active = 1 and workflow_id = 24

condition.expression: NOT CAST(parent_app_country_id IS NULL AS BOOLEAN)
